# Privacy Policy for Idusa

*Effective date:* October 13, 2025  
*Developer:* Amitech  

Idusa is an educational app created by Amitech to help children learn through videos, games, and quizzes.  
This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use the app.

---

## Information Collection and Use
Idusa does *not collect, store, or share any personal data* at this stage.  
All learning content and progress are handled *locally on your device*.  
We do not require users to create accounts or provide any identifiable information.

---

## Permissions
The app may request certain permissions (for example, Internet access) only to load educational content and improve the user experience.  
We do not use these permissions to collect data.

---

## Data Security
Because Idusa currently does not store or transmit user data, there is *no transfer of personal information* to our servers or any third parties.

---

## Upcoming Changes
As Idusa continues to improve, future updates may include optional account features or data syncing to enhance personalization.  
If this happens, the Privacy Policy will be updated and clearly communicated to users before any change takes effect.

---

